{"word":"Heifer","slug":"heifer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Heifer</b> When used as sacrifice, must be without blemish and must not have come under the yoke<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=2'>Num 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=3'>Deu 21:3</a><br/> An atonement for murder<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=9'>Deu 21:9</a><br/> The red heifer used for the water of separation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19'>Num 19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=13'>Heb 9:13</a><br/> Used for draught<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=14&verse=18'>Jdg 14:18</a><br/> Used for treading out wheat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=11'>Hos 10:11</a><br/> Tractable<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=11'>Hos 10:11</a><br/> Intractable<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=16'>Hos 4:16</a><br/><a href='S:Kine'>Kine</a>; <a href='S:Offering'>Offering</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of backsliders<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=4&verse=16'>Hos 4:16</a> <br/> - Of the obedient<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=11'>Hos 10:11</a> "}]}